snippet.title: Top 10 Nerd
snippet.description:
Top 10 Nerd is a dynamic and fun-filled YouTube channel containing nerd-centric videos that has cultivated a dedicated audience we call the #nerdsquad. We are a channel that mainly revolves around comic book culture, Harry Potter, Star Wars, and more!

For business inquiries, please contact Top10NerdChannel@gmail.com
